nl.strohalm.cyclos.entities.customization.fields

Class CustomFieldValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.strohalm.cyclos.entities.Entity
      • nl.strohalm.cyclos.entities.customization.fields.CustomFieldValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AdCustomFieldValue, AdminCustomFieldValue, ImportedAdCustomFieldValue, ImportedMemberRecordCustomFieldValue, LoanGroupCustomFieldValue, MemberCustomFieldValue, MemberRecordCustomFieldValue, OperatorCustomFieldValue, PaymentCustomFieldValue

    public abstract class CustomFieldValue
extends Entity
    The association between a custom field and a given entity. The value property is transient, containing one of stringValue or the value of the related possibleValue. Persistent are stringValue (when the field is not enumerated) or possibleValue (when enumerated).
